FBIS4-10844 "drlat075_k_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-075 Daily Report 18 Apr 1994 SOUTH AMERICA Argentina Menem Denies Suffering Heart Problem 18 Apr Menem Denies Suffering Heart Problem 18 Apr PY1804234694 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 2304 GMT 18 Apr 94 PY1804234694 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS Spanish BFN [Text] Buenos Aires, 18 Apr (NA) -- President Carlos Menem tonight denied suffering a heart problem during the past few hours, which, according to persistent rumors, obliged him to undergo an urgent operation. "I am very well; that rumor must have been put about by someone who wants me to die," Menem said a few minutes ago from the Olivos Residence over the state television channel.
